## About the Website

This website is an access point to find lists of previously offered paid internships, paid summer research programs, and scholarships for continuing education in policy and political science. These lists were last updated Summer of 2022 and are not comprehensive but meant as a jumping off point for you to get started on your own search for opportunities. Know that 
